33581805,AI that predicts how users respond to a feature before launching it,2022-11-13T10:40:07Z,Belalmostafa,1,false,false,1,[33581972],<null>,<null>,<null>,"Hi everyone.

It always happens to all of us when building a specific software that we think that a specific feature will kill it, and our users will love it. But after launching it, it turns out the exact opposite.

It happens to the best of us, even when u do customer interviews, and the only way to avoid that is through extensive large-scale customer interviews, and customer analysis with large and experienced teams, which is something that most startups can'
column2:
t afford.

For this reason, I am building an AI SaaS that will let you simulate how your product users will interact and respond to a specific feature before you actually launch it.

I would like to hear your thoughts about the SaaS I am building and what you would love to see in such a tool, or if you even don'
column3:
t think that I should build it.

If you would like to test the tool once its ready for early adopters, please fill this form so that I can reach out to you https:/
